Every great journey begins with a spark, but what truly makes it extraordinary are the struggles, the perseverance, and the vision behind it.✨

When we started 3TENX, we were driven by a belief in solving real, everyday hair problems, and that belief became the foundation of our dream.

But the road wasn’t easy.�There were failures that tested our confidence, rejections that tried to break our spirit, and sleepless nights filled with uncertainty. Each challenge fueled us to push harder, dream bigger, and create something meaningful.

Today, 3TENX stands as more than just a haircare brand—it’s a testament to the power of believing in ourselves, our vision, and the community that supports us. 

A brand born from challenges, built with love, and committed to making haircare effortless and effective for all. 💜

latestPosts.caption:
When I met Shane, he shared something that truly resonated with me: AVEDA, as a brand and as a family, believes in being the “Care Takers of the Care Givers.”

Our hairdressing community—the caregivers—are tirelessly dedicated to enhancing their clients’ well-being. AVEDA honors this by creating products with the healthiest ingredients and formulations, ensuring not only the safety and wellness of the professionals who use them but also the clients who experience them.

But AVEDA is more than a brand or a product line—it’s a way of life. A life built on the pillars of care, sustainability, and wellness, with a deep commitment to environmental leadership. From sourcing responsibly to formulating vegan, cruelty-free products, AVEDA continues to lead the way in creating beauty that doesn’t compromise the health of people or the planet.

This philosophy came to life on the ON HAIR stage at Cosmoprof India 2024 in Mumbai, where we showcased the artistry and innovation of AVEDA with vegan color treatments and styling products. It was an incredible moment to celebrate not just the brand’s creativity but also its mission to empower the caregivers and create sustainable beauty solutions for a better future.

Bringing AVEDA to India is not just about offering products—it’s about building a movement that uplifts the caregivers, inspires consumers, and nurtures our shared world.

#Aveda #Sustainability #CosmoprofIndia #Hairdressing #CareForTheCaregivers #CleanBeauty #EnvironmentalLeadership

Grateful to be part of the Elle Sustainability Awards 2025 in Mumbai 🌿✨

3TENX was proud to be the gifting partner at this prestigious event — an evening that celebrated sustainability, innovation, and the changemakers of the beauty and Bollywood industry.

We’re determined to spread “love at first wash” with 3TENX, and it was truly heartwarming to connect with so many inspiring individuals and amplify awareness around our brand.

Congratulations to all the winners — each of you is driving meaningful change and truly deserving of the spotlight.

Everyone went home with a little piece of 3TENX magic — including our latest 2025 launch: the GLOSS MIST, designed to give that perfect glass-hair finish ✨
